title: It won't let me que for ranked after 6.21 patch
body: When i go to que for ranked it comes up with please wait,  the screen is black and i can't chose a lane, and after a few seconds (around like 10 or so)  it just exits back to the home page and the play button comes back up (time posting is 6:25 am Queensland time)

replies.body:
Hey all,

There was an issue recently that affected ranked queue on OCE, this issue has now been resolved.

Please do let me know if you are continuing to experience these issues.
